-- Melbourne's Population Will Surpass Sydney's Within 30 Years, Review Says
-- Sarah McDonald
-- 2010-04-26T21:33:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/melbourne-s-population-to-surpass-sydney-s-within-30-years-review-says.html

          
          
             Melbourne’s population will be
larger than Sydney’s within 30 years, the Australian Financial
Review reported, citing a report by research group BIS Shrapnel.
Victoria state is building new homes at twice the rate of New
South Wales, the newspaper cited the report as saying.  
